íŸ@c5f00d633860771aa3d13c142db4b2e5f61932f082e6236c670406e2fce77cb2⁄fTitle: title: math product
Path: Examples
Content:
Compute the product of a list of numbers.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [2 3 3 4] | math product
72

```
Compute the product of each column in a table.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [[a b]; [1 2] [3 4]] | math product
